Required GitHub Secrets:
------------------------

Existing (from ipai-odoo-tests.yml):
- Database credentials in service configuration (no secrets needed)

New Required:
1. ANTHROPIC_API_KEY - Claude API for test generation
2. ODOO_TEST_USER - Test user for E2E/performance tests
3. ODOO_TEST_PASSWORD - Test user password
4. N8N_WEBHOOK_URL - n8n webhook endpoint (optional)
5. PLANE_API_URL - Plane API base URL (optional)
6. PLANE_WORKSPACE_SLUG - Plane workspace identifier (optional)
7. PLANE_API_KEY - Plane API authentication (optional)
8. SUPABASE_URL - Supabase project URL (optional)
9. SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY - Supabase service role key (optional)

Optional:
- CODECOV_TOKEN - Codecov upload (recommended)
- K6_CLOUD_TOKEN - k6 Cloud for advanced metrics
- SLACK_BOT_TOKEN - Slack notifications
- PLANE_BIR_PROJECT_ID - Plane project for issue creation

